Put files in "~/Library/Workflows/Mail Rules"

Add "Run AppleScript" rule to mail app to run the "Launch Automator Workflow"

Example Rule:

Description: Open Link
If [all] of the following conditions are met
 - [From] [Contains] <my email address>
 - [Subject] [Ends with] <insert passcode>

Perform the following actions
 - [Mark as Read]
 - [Run AppleScript] "~/Library/Workflows/Mail Rules/Launch Automator Workflow.scpt"
